{"tid":905541,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"PSG隊友又如何？尼馬遭卡雲尼爆鏟後拒示好","createTime":"2018-11-17T08:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T16:37:33.000Z","uid":5190,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"48063b5146e5d463bc6d4e71d65bd2549bb18089","tid":905541,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pO52V3t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpO52V3t.png&h=2f916da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡雲尼和尼馬又發生不和諧一幕幕經典<br />\n<br />\n巴西大戰烏拉圭，這不但是一場南美2強的經典之戰，亦是巴黎聖日耳門兩位前鋒尼馬和卡雲尼的「PSG打吡」。然而，這兩位球會隊友卻上演極不友好的一幕。<br />\n　　比賽進行到第85分鐘，手握1-0領先優勢的巴西控球，拿球的正是巴西頭牌尼馬。尼馬控球在左路邊線處盤帶，此時烏拉圭前鋒卡雲尼高速上前，從尼馬背後試圖搶下皮球。卡雲尼強行衝擊尼馬，雖然讓皮球離開了尼馬腳下，但巨大的衝擊力也讓他撞倒了尼馬，後者翻滾倒地，手捂著腳踝，大吼慘叫，痛苦不堪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/11/17/5/578b2faf88e77ac209b83cc05a5a956c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F11%2F17%2F5%2F578b2faf88e77ac209b83cc05a5a956c.jpg&h=005e340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡雲尼凶狠鏟翻尼馬<br />\n<br />\n另一邊，卡雲尼在這次凶狠攔截後被球證出示黃牌警告，激動的卡雲尼忍不住對著球證大聲吼叫質疑。在冷靜片刻後，卡雲尼試圖上前把倒在地上的尼馬拉起，誰知尼馬毫不領情，一巴掌打開卡雲尼的手，嘴裡唸唸有詞。卡雲尼無可奈何地把球扔給尼馬，嘴裡也說著甚麼回擊尼馬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/11/17/7/70f61884369649a76e7e25f9488edbab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F11%2F17%2F7%2F70f61884369649a76e7e25f9488edbab.jpg&h=183b62db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人又有了小摩擦<br />\n<br />\n卡雲尼和尼馬之間的故事由來已久，在尼馬剛剛加盟巴黎聖日耳門時，二人就曾在球場上公開爭奪12碼、自由球的主射權，也一度把大巴黎的更衣室攪得一團糟，此後二人公開發聲表示相互之間沒有問題，才讓那場風波告一段落。如今，二人又在公開場合鬧出不愉快，不知會對二人的關係造成甚麼樣的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/9433468/1/20181117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F9433468%2F1%2F20181117&d=UfTLgsTyKnhjqbRbQOEjKv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a1f5d73d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/9433468/1/20181117</a>"},{"pid":"c8dfd139a9a144920e00a7e1775fd7e50db9f350","tid":905541,"uid":5190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:05:31.000Z","msg":"卡叔 我疤歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e09a9bfab8cd8cc5108d03c16a432a234ea1bb1","tid":905541,"uid":31744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8dfd139a9a144920e00a7e1775fd7e50db9f350","tid":905541,"uid":5190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:05:31.000Z","msg":"卡叔 我疤歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"用牙蘇交換ok?"},{"pid":"a0ab1f0a46ffbe631a89e075187b620a5c50cf66","tid":905541,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e09a9bfab8cd8cc5108d03c16a432a234ea1bb1","tid":905541,"uid":31744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8dfd139a9a144920e00a7e1775fd7e50db9f350","tid":905541,"uid":5190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:05:31.000Z","msg":"卡叔 我疤歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"用牙蘇交換ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"團聚呀"},{"pid":"c16d8f3fd67846281db74322e0eb8e93b0004a59","tid":905541,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7150db9d2ea717086e410bfc9286ed1b33d9e3b8","tid":905541,"uid":10670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"卡雲尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/suppor